Create a learning video game which the aim of the game is to collect letters and create words at the end of the game based on letters 
you have collected.
Based on this, everybody can learn vocabularies in foreign languages. 

We want to open one part of the game: 
 - Everybody can change the content and the end of the game. For example, if somebody wants to add new steps at the end, it's possible. 
 
 
 
